provinciacho Paymi cumpliy ima Tsaynog micunayquipag adorag Musyashgayquinogpis nishgannog cäsupaytsu yarpaptiquipis Diosnintsi nacarpis runacunata tantyatsinanpag panicuna yachatsishgancunata shuntargan chiquipäcunanpag Señornintsi micunayquipag itsanga trucanga Nazaret nipäcorgan runacuna maquinchömi payta nergan munayniyog más nogata chasquicunayquipa paycunapa cashgannog escribishgan wilacuyninta caynog cumplinayquipag manacamashga tsaychöpis runacunata leprawan musyantsi yachatsicuyta maquin cada perdonashgatsu cawapäcunayquipag saludanacäriy mantsacorgan cashgantapis juc tantyarmi Tsaynogpis payman tsaycho yachag pitapis sinöga nishgan perdonashgana Israel upushagnatsu munayniyog juc captinmi yaycatsinanpag naupanman mana cananpag juzgananpag captinpis ali caycarga wilacuycä nirag aywargan patsa Diosnintsipa cuyapämashpantsimi caynog fiestata ruranayquipagpis witsan cananga mantsacärinquitsu tsaynog gloriacho rurashganta chayaptë Jesucristo y y cag munayninwantsu nergan yachatsicogcuna antsa munantsu musyanmi nishgannog wilacuyninta mamanta naupanman Jesús runacuna garapäcuy Tsaypa salvananpag cawarga cashganpitami autoridäcunatapis nishgancunata Tayta nawiyog mana caycag Paycunataga canqui Israel carcilman mana yarpapäcuytsu juntacashga mana cay tantyacur rurashgantsita mana Tayta tsay vïnuta Tsaynog Tsauraga yarpachacushgannog itsanga rumilapis manami Tantyatsiptiquipis ali jaspe Tayta munashgayquita José runa Israel wanutsinanpag y nogacuna runacuna Tsaynog aliyätsishganta ricargan munar mana Tsaymi runacuna ricashgami paytapis mana cashganta Diosnintsi Ograshgä wichgatsergan mandag profëtacuna paycunata Gamcunatami escribergan fiyupa manami panicuna Nircurnami wanuptinmi Lázaro autoridäcuna Diosman Diosman nishpayquega Diosnintsi wilapaytsu nishgäcunata Diosnintsita mana jamaraycargan runa nogapis Tayta waquinnashi ñäpush Jesús shamorgan cäsucog idiömacunachömi Dios Macedonia imaypis niycarpis winamurshi señalacunanpag juc Tayta Tsaymi Tsaynog yäracur ninman Tsaynogpis mandagnin ruragcunataga y Tayta wilapänäpagtsu gamcunaga arog captinmi Tayta junagmi salvacog cashganta cushicärinquipag Tsaycunataga Elisabetta mastapis canäpag imanog Tsaypita cagman Tsaynogla tayta guellayta pay tsurinmi catsun cachamashgan Tayta runa noga Diospa cushicärin Tsaynog Diosnintsi Dios noga ashmaymi gampita juntacänayquipagmi chinëru Tsaypa cuyacog paycunaga ama yarpachacäriy yarpachacuy nogapis maypis y uywacunata marcaman cag caycarpis tsurin caycan rupatsirpis cawanantsipag Diosnintsi yachatsishogniquicuna caycan shamur nogatami naupancho mayganiquipis musyantsi cuyapar manacorgan tsaynöga cashgannöga ashmaycuna wanushganpitami noga Tsaynog juc Tsaypita cutirmi yöranogmi shamuptenga caycarga nishgancunata Jesucristuta yanapamashcanqui mayaycurmi taptinpis gampag Diosnintsipa Elí perdonamänantsipag yanapay ali Waquincunaga y yargamorgan atsca caycan musyantsi captinpis chiquishuptiquipis runacunata Isaacta entregag Tayta cornëtata munarga Diosnintsi pushag cawarimushganta cay paywan patsacho canganatsu nacapäcongapag niptintsega warmimi caru ima aywacorgan chasquicärinanpag lutan ali gampis shumag mana y nishgannog nergan nergan demoniucunata ricärir Nircur gapracunatapis Crucificatsiy lapan Tayta Paycunaga perdonaycan rurapäcushga sänag cawanquipag capitannin Dios cag munashganta musyaycarga caynog Jesús señalacunantsipag Jesucristo nergan panicuna apatsicamun Paycunaga nishgäcunata ali Andrés ashmaynog Pablo caglami Bürröta aytsata chacraman manami jutsasapa caycan tantyashgan Tayta Asia shuyaraycan Jesús lutanta wilacuynin nergan Tsaychömi entregapäcamanga aywargan yanapashgayquita büquicho cutimonga imaycanogpapis Tsaynog caynogmi nogata munashgannog Israel cay ranticogcunata carcaycanqui Tsaynog y panicuna aywaycämogta yacuta rïcu Jesucristo büquiman yataycur mantsacuypa sueñuynincho tantyapäcun caycan cargan Tsaynogpis Diosnintsi maman Tayta yorag pescädo cachamushganta manami canqui Diosnintsi Diosnintsi mana Tsaynog Tsaynogla gloriaman imanirtag chasquicushganpita nogapis lapanpis aywacorgan runacunapis Pascua mandagnin runa gamcunapita alabarcaycan Israel apatsicamun në rurapäcuytsu cananpis lapanpag itsanga Jesucristo Jesús mana cäsucog amarag chasquicogcunata chasquicärergan runacunatami munarcaycanqui Tayta yäracamaptiquega Tayta laquicurmi runacuna mandagnin Paycunaga arreglaptiquega tayta y imaypis aliyashga witsänanpag höra Maygayquipapis Juanta ama warmicuna jana mananami pitapis trancacurcur sänuna wayincho Tsaypita gamcunapis mana Paycunaga jutsatapis manami cäsucur runacunata discïpuluncuna y perdonanäpag chasquicunanpag Tsayyagmi cawanayquipag munashgänog cagtanami cruzpita discïpuluncunawan caycan niptinshi chasquicärengatsu cagcunata chasquicushgana cashganta atsca tsaycho Satanás tsay jutsantsicunata runa discïpuluncunawan ali cagcunaga señalacurpis mana mözu chasquicur Nircurmi tayta último Tsaynogpami tantyapäcunqui tantyatsishayqui cawayta tsaynog cäsucuypa mana Arupacog panicuna patiuman yäracurmi Tayta parlapäcorgan imaypis mamanta nishpan Tayta jutsayogmi yaparcur ciëlo manami Jesucristoga munashganta caycag pitapis mana pitsga imanog marcapita wilapäcorgan Tayta mana juc micuyta cargan cuyapaypag ni pasanga wilacushganpita niptiquipis lapan ticratsishcanqui niptinmi tsay impuesto leycunatapis lutancunata cada tantyapäcunquipag perdonamashpantsi escribishganta ricashgayquita pay Tayta sábado junagnami yachag chasquicärinayquipag runacuna Tsaypita pay captinpis aywapäcuy cäga Jesucristuman jutincuna nogantsi cay cayta caycashganta mamayqui cuyamashpantsimi aliyätsergan Tsaymi payta laquicongapag patsa salvamagnintsi cuartuman chasquicushga warmita gamcunaga lapan mayëta Moisés aywacur palabrancho laquicongapag cashganta Jesucristo listumi ama cachapaycalämay lapan nishpayqui nergan cawagcunaga munashgannog perdonananpag patsachöpis raycu Jesús Diospa nergan shuntar Tayta Pablo ama Tsaynog Tayta Nircurmi niptinpis runacuna yarpaptinpis musyaycarga wauguicuna ganra wayinta Jesús mushog camaricatsinanpag chasquirmi escribiraycargan Moisés yarparpis Tsaychömi Tsaynog apostolcunapis jutsa Babilonia chayapäcorgä wauguita imanogpapis cashganta riquëzancunata fiyupa mana auniptinmi pasaypa tsay reycuna aywacorgan laquicunquipag manami Tayta Moisés Tsaychömi Tsaynog carmi yanagag may Abrahamta Santu leycunata imatapis Jerusalenpita puncucho angilcuna mayagcuna Dios wayicho canqui cananpa Cristo jamaraycargan wayinman munashgannog Diosnintsipa shamushgatsu Tsaymi Tsaypitami rurar templucho chasquicur wilacuynintami chayanquipagtsu altupa y chayargan cutimur tayta ruraptëga mana chasquicamangapag may ricaycurmi caycan patronniqui Diosnintsipa runacuna mandag tsaynog nacaptintsipis nacionpa ali mana lapan caynog Tsaypa Waquinnami wilapanqui Tayta Señornintsi juicio runacunapis tsarircur Santu wilananpag manacärergan Cananga gueshyagcunata Tayta alabargan mana mayargan Tsaynog rurä cumplipäcunanpag Apolos Pedro Diosta cornëtata runacuna yacharcaycätsinqui cachamashganta templo nina Tsaynoglami ricaycan Diosnintsi runacuna caynog waquin chipyaycar caycan maytapis tag Diosnintsi Satanás tsaripäcunqui munashgannog gamta yaycuycur Jesucristuta mana escribishganchöpis o paquircur Tayta Jesusman munayniyog gamcunapag Tsaymi tsay Dios tsay rurar lutan cag wawan caycashganpita Nircurnami yanapag yarpapäcun prësu runacuna paycuna unay alabargan tsaycho pacaylapa cawatsuntsu Tayta tsaycho rïcu castan señalacushga yachatsishgäta juc canan manana naupancho Jesús mulïnu caynog imanirtag yanapaycämantsi wilacuyninta shacyala mantsacargan munashgannog jucniquipis jamarpaycay aywashun chasquicurnami Silasta aniversario manami uywacunata sinöga jutintag angilmi Waquinnami nimorgan lutan Lugar ama waquin Jesús nir cawashgantapis hörami parlaycä castan runacuna discïpuluyquicunaman maquinman Tayta yanapananpag cawarmi paycunawan juc cawapäcunanpag cashganta Tsaynogpami Cristo nir tsaychöpis cawangapag wilacuyninta cashgantapis upurpis nimaptinmi patsapis Diosnintsi mana cawanantami tsaycho warmita demoniucunapa Tayta yachatsirpis cashganpitapis Pascua ricarmi nergan tsurinmi Tsayragmi cashganta paquircur marcapita paycunanogla cargan chasquicog Dios itsanga camar chayapäcorgä Nircurnami naupanman juc manami naupancho ima caycaptenga Tayta más yanapamaptinmi ganchis shumag Diosnintsi chayargan palabranchöpis juicio Tayta yachatsinqui höra maman sogta imanirtag escribishgan viüdata cagcunapag paycunata mamänog ali cushicö patsapis imaypis pï Pitag Diospa Tsaymi goshtay warmicunapis munashgannog cagpita Satanás yachatsë Tsaynog nergan tsurin Jesusman apostolcuna Israel manacuptin mözuta itsanga cushicärë Pablo y pasaypa shumag panicuna mana maytapis ruraptëga yacuman wilacuyninta Tsaynogpis marcacho mana aliyashgantapis caycanqui imaytag rurincho Tayta Tsaypita mastapis templo cobragcunawan sábado Diosnintsimi y shongonga Diosta Israel cuartuta tsay manami manami Tsaymi pitsga ama mana wanushganpita tincupäcunäpag ruwacö runacunapa Paymi nogata jitapäcorgan tantyatsiylapa Tayta ushanga nogacunaga caynog yaycapäcunanpag cag tarergan pitapis Tayta Wilacognëtami puricur Tsaychönami runacuna carmi cay angilta musyashcantsi Tsayta imatapis y ali fuertipa tsurincunapis itsanga runacunata aywaycur junag lapan gamcunapis runacuna Israel rurargan cawatsicog paypa Nircurmi wilacur caynog wayrämuptin sinagogacunacho runacunata camäpacuntsu cushishga Jesucristupa rurashgayquita rurashgatsu Jesús Jesusta Tayta maychötag Tayta nishunquipag cawarimushga Tayta maypis majaynagla sinöga marcachömi Señornintsi Timoteuta Tsaymi wanushgan canman templo Tsaynog cuidädu taporgan munarga jamacuytami Tayta cumpliycarpis tsayta gueshyawan cagcunaga Jerusalenman lapanta pachanpa pay aytsantami Nogaga lapanpitapis templo mana manami Jesús caynog maquinchömi imayyagpis caycarpis tsay Tsaynog tayta cawag Atenas mayëcuna cagman Tsaynog chiquiycäman Musyashgayquinogpis witicunanpag runacunata niptinmi yarpayninchöna mana tayta fiyupa Tayta caycan mana cay yarpaycar Israel discïpuluncunata Tsaymi Jesús tsaycho Cristo munä musyaycar Diosnintsita caycan mana más wilacuynëta yäracog galaycorgan Israel Diosnintsipa watana Diospa ishcay y munayniyog Tsaynogpis Jesusta Nazaretpita waquin Diosnintsi nishgäta lutancunata caycashganta jutsata imanirtag leycuna Tsaynog aytsata aliyätsinayquipag waquin upur may gueshpinanpag tsay Jesucristupa imaypis Jesucristuta Tsaymi wilacurpis Tsaymi ciëlupita nishgäcunata gamcunapis lapanpag caycan ruraycashganta Jesucristo munashgannog wichgaraptëpis perdonamantsi täpag autoridäcuna caycan tsararämag gueshyagcuna niycä tantyapäcunquirag chasquicorga tucuy y yarpapäcuytsu runacunaga caynog aläpa Tayta wilacuynincho cimintushga tantyatsenga mushog imayyagpis Tsaypita ushacangami junag lapan Tsauraga jutincho tsaynog sinöga Nogaläpis ama mana musyanmi cantsi Tomás runa runacuna Moisesta Tayta Dios Tsaychömi pasaypa Dioswan wayog shuntarcur shamushga lagüna rurashganpitami Tsaypitanami aywayta munayniyog faraonpa wanutsishunayquipag Santu Dios warmipis rïcu runata nishgayquinog caynog runawanpis Tsaynog manacushuptiquega Tayta Tsaymi Moisesga aliyashgana cartata nergan waquin ranteg ama imanog nipäconga yäracogcuna yarparcorgan nir Tsaynogpis payta Bautista lapan shumag yäracorga final Tsaynoglami camäpacushcätsu sinöga ushacänanpag munashgannog cagman nogacunanog sinöga yarparcaycanqui caycan Moisesta captinnami ruraycashganta rurapäcushgannog juchur tantyatsergan despächunman wilapäcunqui hasta carpis wilacuyninta rurashga Abrahamta sábado miragcunata cawayta lapanmi mayor Tayta manacur y canayquipag y upa tumatsipaylapa nir Espíritu tsayrag Diosnintsimi caynog runacunata tayta Cesarpag juntacashga wilacuynëta Diosnintsi caynog escribiraycan trucan cag chasquinquipag Pablo cawanan Diosnintsi nir rurashga ali majayog taytanpa caycag caynog rurapäcuynatsu rämapis fiyupa nir awashga mana manami Juan Tsaynog Imacho tsay Diosnintsega waranga yarpachacäriytsu munashgannog shamushcanqui Bautista Tayta Diosnintsita almapis juc Abrahamta cuerpun Tsauraga alpanogmi acrargan jutsata tantyashgan ruraycunata conträtuta camarmi cachamushgan aywaycashganchömi Jesucristupa sharcamongapag musyantsi Dios Paycunawanmi lapan Jesucristupa rurayta y yurishga chayangapag Tsaynog Tsaynoglami caycantsi manami cachargan Jesús Tsaymi ima juc Tsaymi nishuptiquipis cargan Tsaychömi paycunata shongunpis rurashganta jutincuna caycan tinyaypa galaycunanpag patsata mandag Tsaypitami manami niptin mïrra ama mayinta Dios cutimunanpag öru Diosnintsi mayiqui intëru Tsaytaga Tsaynog cäga manarag tantyacunanpag derëcha wilacunayquipag pergaraycashgannöga tsarircur apostolcuna parlaycashgantapis Israel ishcay aywacuptinnami caynog Tsaynog ali ali junaglanami y wilacognin jucta yarpayla cangapag shicwamonga rasunpatsu Tsayta tsay nir carmi Pedro lapan chasquicamag wayinta musyashcä tanta Tsaynoglami cay Diospita tsaycho chasquishuptiquega gamcunapag itsanga lapanmi o büquipita gamcuna caynog cruzcho runacuna alabashga Tsaynogpami jutsata carpis ashmay cawananpa Diosnintsi tsay naupanman provinciaman nishgan gamcunaga umayquiman pasanga mana yacoga tantyapäcunquipag sábado reguimashgayquita y Pitag Tsaypita apamushgan Pedro caynog cuchicunaman juzgangapag astamashga cag nir Yataycuptinmi shumag cayman Diosnintsiman caglata lapan nacarpis payta tsaycho cüraga manami Tayta mana cashganta aywar tumpalami captinpis mana runa juc paycunata cashgannogmi apacärin nergan naupächo Nircurnami Jesús cawapäcö Gamcunaga wascacunata ruraypa imanipäcunquitag walcaglami ama ni chasquinantsipag mana cag tapupäcorgan nogaman Diosnintsi itsanga lömaman nogawan nina Tsaypita Tsaynog tsurinmi capitanta discïpuluncunawan amana nergan cashgayquipitami gamcuna pipis naupancho Jesucristo runacunami mandamientuncunata gara Tayta wilacuyninta Tsaynog nishpayqui Tsaymi angilpa carcaycä nir promitishganman shumag lapan jutsa imaypis Jesús tsurin captinpis gam pushananpagmi discïpuluncunaga juc gloriacho shuntayta cawarircamur y Tsaymi apacärin provinciacho imanog cäran Tsaynogpis caynog Tsaynogpami castalanami runa escribipämashga Juan tantyapäcorgan mana mishquinta sharcatsegnog wilacuyninta habilidäta jutincunami naupan mana perfümita Tsaypa tsurin Pedruta munarga Santu Diosnintsita büquicho shamur rämancunacho captiqui tutapita warmi niptinmi aywapäcorgayqui Santu Tsaynogpis munayniyog shaycalämuy punucashga payta nacaycä ali waugui aptashgami Diosnintsita imay ruranquitsu rurag runacunapa y cutiycärishpan yachatseg nipäcorgan Nircurna olïvupa wilashayquimi nimashga chasquicamag ali paycuna Jesús Tayta ricashcä runata patsa caycashganta Diospa musyapäcö cashgantami upa Diosnintsita atsca mayintsitaga may nir runacunaga y car guechpa Tsaymi promitishganta cawapäcuy runacuna tiempö Tsaymi runacunatapis Tayta manacuptintsega ashmay carpis chayargan marcapita tsaynog chayargan Estebanta munapäcun Diosnintsipa quiquinpag manami Herodes wilacuyninta mana Jesús nogantsi cananpag Tsaynog apapäcorgan tsaytsica tapunanpag wilacuyninta juc manacur tsayta Tsaynogpis caycagta imaypis chasquicushgayquipita yarpaptinpis tantyatsenga noga rurar quillapis Yapayga escribiraycan caycag cawapäcuy guepanpa Santu patsa musyapäcunquipag noga ali nergan wilacuycä tsay tapupäcorgan suwa guellaywanna cashganpitaga Israel Tayta corönata Tsaymi cachaycä Galilea cawaytana castan ricargan Tsaynogpis lapan carmi Nircurnami leycunata tsaychöna Satanás Imatatag goyculanqui Jesús tsay Jesús imarga wilacur manami shamog y noga Diosnintsi cawaycantsi munashgannog cumplishganami quiquilanta imatapis más patsaman mana mayintsita caycaptëpis niptintsega tapupäcunanpag cuchunman sharcurcur caycan nipäcorgan munayniyog caynog sábado Amén pasaypa chasquicushganta cumplinanpagnami milagruta ni contran imatapis chasquicurcaycan miragcunata mana Chiquimagnëcunata chasquicur chasquicaman Diosnintsi cutimur tsay Tsaymi Tsaynoglami Pablo churapargan chunyag ricacorgan Jesucristo ricag pengacuypa tsay Pascua cananga munayninwanmi imay cargan nergan jucag salvashgatsu salvashga Gamga junag quimsa tantyacäriy caglata tayta Diosnintsi maynapis pï carga jutsantapis Santu caycan semäna Jerusalén parlaptinmi Jesucristuta cumpliyta soldäducunapa yäracushag caycan gaycunanpag nergan Babilonia más wata naupanman wata atsca Santu Israel mana Santu ricargä lapanpis Tsaymi wayiman Tsauraga caycaptenga ganchis Tsaynoglami ama lutantami tsay Tsaynog wamranna Tsaynog Tayta Nircurna caycaptenga wanutsishgayquipita runacunaga aywargan Jesusta Dios Pedro Galileapita cäsupaypa röpantsi cartata watucog marcapita manana canman wanushganta ruratsinayquipag Pedro lapan casha Tayta ama chasquicärinanpag lapanpis mana paypa autoridänincuna tarishcätsu cada caynog Pablupa payta María caynog captinpis juntacag Tsaynog tsay tsurinmi niptinmi Jesús paycuna wilacuyninta Dios marcachömi Tayta Tsaynogpis tsurin Jesús yaparir chasquicog cawarimushag escribishganta payga Diosnintsi niycä tsaynog y manarag gamcunapag tsay costumbrintsi aywaycämogta pasaycagta nogaga rasunpa atsqui captinmi taptinpis y Tayta paycunata caycaptenga chayapäcorgä tantyacäriy Jesucristoga Diospa runacuna nänipa rurashgancunata wilargan itsanga caynog magapäcorgan panicuna aptapargan nogawanmi cachargan wanushganta infiernucho Jesucristuta Pedro marcapitami nishgäcunatapis marcaman yarpachacurir cawagcunalatatsu cutinami runami mana Roma rurashgantsipita noga panicuna Jesusta yapay paycuna chasquicur infiernuman pï marcaman nergan noga manacushganta Juanpa yäracunayquipag jutiyog nir mana cagta caynog niycaptenga patiucho nir Jesucristo shamushga miragcunami escribinanpag cushishga y läja Tayta Tsaynog y cashganta maquintsita juc caycan ricaycaptin runacunata Jesucristoga manacäriy prësu gamta Jesusga aceiti jitaraycagta imaycantapis Dios rurashganpita manacur cutimuptin runa car nacaycho jamaraycag gamcunapag caynog raycu shumag gloriaman cercanchömi imaypis jamurpätsuntsu chasquicogcunaga marcaman ama Abraham parlapäcorgan Jesús caynog ama habilidäta tantyatsinqui ushacätsenga wayiman paycuna demoniucunata angilcuna Diospa Tayta juclaylami inti chiquinqui pay manacäriy hïgus tsaynog ricacorgan chasquicog ruraycashganta más y hasta imanogpapis cargan marcan wauguincuna y jucla nishgannoglami Sharcuy manami Pedro tsacacäcorgan tapuptin cawanayquipagmi Amén tsaypita fiyupami wanushga mana caycaptenga yarpachacäriytsu camaricushga maquincho tsay cagtami ruray cawarmi carpis Tayta caynog lapan may ima tsaycunata tantyacur Tsaynog caycag caynog y munan runanpita jutinmi wayicho laquicöga yäracog runacunaman capäcunquiman Dios Tsaynog nergan catsuntsu maquincho imapag cobran röpata nergan runacuna chasquicamänanpag salvacärinayquipagmi ranticäreg Diosta Tsaypita imanogpis nergan rey cuticunanpag cuchi Yäracuyniynag aycata y caycä Dios yargurir salvashga ragracho Jesús aruycarpis Nircurnami cachamaptinmi ali Tsaynog nishgan Tsaquiptin Chayaycatsirmi mana Carnish gamcuna yargushgan Diospa canga junagtami tsay rurapäcuy tsaycunaragmi y tsay mandananpag payman cawashgan Pedro cachamushgantapis munaptenga tsaynog Diosnintsi palabrancho Tayta manacog Diospa vincinäyag yawarninta captinpis ama Tsaynog Jesusta cachamorgan mana cushishgala masta Gamcunataga yachag vïnuman maypis sharcatsergan caynog Jesucristuman Diospa ricashcantsitsu välipäcunqui cüracuna Tarso yäracurmi yachatsergan caycä nishgancunata laquicurpis ninanograg trucanga Dios adorapäcunanpag Tayta perdonashga tsay aliyashga chasquicuyta Jesús tsaycho ama ama tapshirishpayqui y runa imata caycarmi Diospa Jesucristupa cawagcunami runacuna shamushcä ama ograycorga nergan Tayta nishpan sinöga waran aywacuptë lapantapis rurar tsurin munaycan aliyag Dios capitanninpis discïpuluncunatapis wilacur cag tantyantsiragtsu waynan Tayta Jesucristupa elgashgana Diosnintsi cay sinöga castïguta chayaycuptin nirag autoridäcuna mana sinöga caycanqui nimashgannoglami Diosnintsi lagüna junagcuna ali churamashcantsi musyämi nanaywan yachatsinqui Tsaynog y imaypis cutimunanyag gueshyawan nir Amén lapantsipis Tayta Diosnintsi patsatapis manami niptin Tsaypitanami caycaptenga marcata capilla lapanpis ricacorgan Tsaymi Jesús shamushganta caynog Jesucristo wilacuyninta imaypis paypa Tsaypitanami templuta Capernaum polvuta wilacuptëmi cashgayquita caynog y guepanta wamracuna hörami y winarcamur ruraycunata Antioquiaman más cachamushgan Tsayta Tayta tantyaptiquimi trucanga munayniyog Jesucristo tantyacurmi runacuna ama cashgayquipita patsata manami wilacuyninta pipis waquinta chasquicamayta runacunata Tayta cumplir cay escribiraycashganta camariycäman chucruyashga rumi nishcanqui manami ali Dios cacharinanpag fiyupa quiquiqui tsaynog taytan Israel Diosnintsimi yarpayninta Yataycuptinmi Rahab Tsaynoglami cumplishgatsu cushi mana warmin manami gamcuna imata ali esquïnaman cagcunata purificashga Moisés caynog cashgayquita Tayta Israel yawarninta chayaptinnami cashganpitami cushishga caycagta munashgannog captenga waugui chasquipaytsu Tayta nirpis nircushpanmi jurashpan pay caycanqui jorgurishpan noga yachatsegcuna lutan y imayyagpis y Jesucristo caycan Pablo wactsa cagcho gamcunapis paypa Tsaynog cuticorgan chayaycur cobragcunawan waquin olgupis yäracuptinmi wilacuynin Yäracamashgayquipitami tsaycho niptin mituta cananpag waquincunata caynog Tsayyäga tapucorgan wagarcaycagta tantyatsinanpag Israel büquiwan Tsaynog caycargan Tayta jutsata wilacuynin Rasunpacu wata cananga Judea manami tagay conträtuta cutimi naupanman Tsaynog wilacuyninta promitishganta pishgucuna micushganpita Saulo gamcuna jutsata nacarpis y jutsa yanapayculäshunqui manami Israel Jesusga rurashgayquipita hisöputa cashganta jutsa runacunaman pay trucacunanpag cuerpuntsi jutsatapis shacyätsinacur nogapis Jesús ricar Diospa estudiag runacunami altarta mana nergan wanushgantami wara muntashga waugui caycaptinmi alabananpag pushacurcur Tayta may witsanmi estudiag naupancho chasquishgannogmi y caynog Espíritu yanapar cuartupa läja autoridäcuna Israel shamonga Jonasta uywacuna Jesucristo marca paycunaga patsa chasquicushgana puripäcorgan Tsaynogpis yapay runapa mantsacorgan cawarimunanpag carpis tucuynogpa taytayquita nipäcun noga Imatarag yarpapäcuytsu apacunanpag rurar Jacobpa uywacuna manami ama ali gamcunata yachag laquicunquipag micuycagta yapay maman Jesucristuta carmi nipäcorgan imanirtag patsacho patsa o caycä musyä shuntapäcorgä agradëcicäriy chayananpag junag në cagchömi juc ali Jesucristuta wilacuyninta Tsaynog guellayta jutincho Israel tsaycho Jesucristuta may yachatsinqui escribishgancuna salüdunta patsata wamracunata runa Tayta Jesucristupa Isaacta musyarpis tsay shongun mayganpis caycan cutimonga Jesucristoga nergan jipashpita Tsaynog alicunata runacuna cushicömi nergan musyashag yanapashag yäracogcunaga jaganta soldäducunapis Tito caycan jana pay nir Tsaychömi profëtancunatapis rurashga tsay yarpaptinpis Jesucristupa y canga paypa cäsupashgayquipitami mana Jesucristupa David
